Text: This "movie" is a piece of crap. Seriously, dont waste your time, its so low budget and the "actors" are crappy, it hurts watching it. I deleted it after a few minutes of watching it.

Bruce Dern, (father of Laura Dern - Jurassic Park, played the Botanist Dr. and friend of Sam Neels character), makes me suspect to the accusations of these actors being total crap. Bruce Dern is by no means a "CRAP actor". He's been in hundreds of movies, and is even a winner of a couple of OSCARS. He is known as playing psychopaths and criminals in general.
